In order to execute the application follow these steps:
	1. run the Bridges Java class
	2. run the ControlRoom Java class
	3. run the City Java class.
	
If you want to modify the number of bridges:
	1. change the NBRIDGES variable value in the Bridges Java class
	   to select how many pairs of traffic lights create
	2. change the NBRIDGES variable value in the City Java class
	   to tell how many bridges the citizens can choose from
	3. change the NBRIDGES variable value in the ControlRoom Java class
	   to create the controllers for all the bridges.
	   
If you want to modify the number of citizens change the N variable in the 
City Java class.

If you want to change the swapping period change the T variable value in the
ControlRoom Java class.